  <brief_title>Correlation of In-lab Pleural Fluid Glucose Measurements With a Finger Stick Glucometer and Portable Point of Care Testing Device (i-STAT).</brief_title>
  <official_title>Correlation of In-lab Pleural Fluid Glucose Measurements With a Finger Stick Glucometer and Portable Point of Care Testing Device (i-STAT).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
